 second he spent worrying was every  second  he  spent  using  up  his
 credits  and  now this well here was one time someone wasn't going to
 collect he took a drink and watched a plane make its way  across  the
 sky  lights  blinking hello and good-bye off in the distance he could
 still see a vehicle of some kind making its way towards him the  dust
 surrounding  it  staining the countryside red OK you tell me why it's
