 working the cop's swollen member when she bit down hard  he  stumbled
 back  screaming  she  got to her feet and started to run fighting the
 pain on his  face  he  pulled  his  gun  and  fired  the  first  shot
 shattering  her  skull blowing bits of bone brains and blood over the
